{{for|the film based on the book|Miracles from Heaven (film)}} {{Infobox book | name = Miracles from Heaven (milagros en el cielo) | author = Christy Beam | image = | caption = | country = United States | language = English | genre = Religious Drama | publisher = | release_date = April 14, 2015 | media_type = Print (Paperback, hardcover) | pages = | isbn = 0316381810 | website = }}
'''''Miracles from Heaven: A Little Girl, Her Journey to Heaven, and Her Amazing Story of Healing''''' is a memoir written by an American author Christy Beam, released on April 14, 2015. The author wrote the book about her daughter Annabel Beam.<ref>{{cite news|title='Miracles From Heaven': Near-Fatal Fall Cures Sick Little Girl's Symptoms|url=http://insider.foxnews.com/2015/04/14/miracles-heaven-near-fatal-fall-cures-sick-little-girls-symptoms|accessdate=July 20, 2015|work=foxnews.com|date=April 14, 2015}}</ref>
== Plot == The book is about the author's 10-year-old daughter Annabel Beam, who was diagnosed with a rare terminal stomach disorder. While on a visit home from the hospital she fell while climbing a tree with her older sister, a branch gave way sending Annabel 30 feet down headfirst into the hollow trunk of a cottonwood tree. She was inside the trunk of the tree for several hours where she visits with Jesus who tells her she will be fine. She is finally rescued and taken to a hospital. She woke up at the hospital without any broken bones or internal injuries. After this incident, she no longer felt pain due to her stomach disorder and her doctor confirmed that her rare disease was somehow miraculously cured.
== Film adaptation == {{main article|Miracles from Heaven (film)}} [[Sony Pictures Entertainment]] has produced a film adaptation, starring [[Jennifer Garner]], [[Kylie Rogers]], [[Queen Latifah]], [[Martin Henderson]], and [[Eugenio Derbez]]. It is directed by [[Patricia Riggen]] and scripted by Randy Brown.<ref>{{cite news|last1=Kit|first1=Borys|title='Heaven Is for Real' Producers Reteam for Sony's 'Miracles From Heaven' (Exclusive)|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/heaven-is-real-producers-reteam-747889|accessdate=July 15, 2015|work=hollywoodreporter.com|date=November 10, 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=MIRACLES FROM HEAVEN Starring Jennifer Garner, Martin Henderson, Kylie Rogers, Eugenio Derbez & Queen Latifah Begins Filming in Atlanta|url=http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/miracles-from-heaven-starring-jennifer-garner-martin-henderson-kylie-rogers-eugenio-derbez--queen-latifah-begins-filming-in-atlanta-300114203.html|accessdate=July 19, 2015|work=[[PR Newswire]]|date=July 17, 2015}}</ref>
