 Dogs" || ''All Due Respect'' |- |[[James L. Ross]] || "The Gypsy Ring" || ''[[Alfred Hitchcock's Mystery Magazine]]'' |- |[[Tim L. Williams]] || "Promissory Notes" || ''[[Ellery Queen's Mystery Magazine]]'' |- |[[Elizabeth Zelvin]] || "A Breach of Trust" || ''[[Mysterical-E]]'' |-
